metadata.name: Factory sketches #40
metadata.description:
This landscape portrays an urban scene with factories in the background, in monochromatic tones that add a sense of nostalgia and melancholy to the scene, evoking the idea of an abandoned or declining city. But not everything is sadness in this landscape, some birds fly over the scenery, bringing a touch of lightness and freedom to the scene.
Developed in p5.js.

metadata.name: Electric Hope #254
metadata.description:
Perceived as fabric of dark and vivid thoughts, hope is always there. Sparse layers of squares form an intricate colorful lattice reflecting mixed feelings of hopelessness and hopefulness, doubt and optimism.

Press S to save. To download in custom size (ex. 2000px width), add &size=2000 to url, reload and press S.

Inspired by CMYK halftone printing patterns

Made with p5js especially for #fxhashturnsone event. 50% of primary sales will be donated to Processing Foundation

metadata.name: Reflecting pools #100
metadata.description:
In a space that reflects and refracts, an invitation to contemplation and reflection. 
Project created in p5.js.

metadata.name: Rubik's Cube #65
metadata.description:
A rubik's cube starts with random sets of moves, see if you can get a perfectly solved cube !

Press Number 1 ~ 6 to rotate Top, Bottom, Left, Right, Front and Back
Press the spacebar to solve the cube. ( It's solved by reverting all the moves. I unfortunately don't know how to solve a rubik's cube :) )


Have fun and Good Luck !
